<experience cog:lid='experience'>
    A latent fear attends me, through all my activities, often stabbing me without warning
    </experience>



<rational_interpretation cog:lid='rational'>
    My fear is that I am proving to be unequal to the demands of practical reason;
    that I am breaking faith with the past and living in ultimate futility
    <temporal_aspects>
        <past>
            In part I fear that I am breaking faith with the past,
            failing those who came before me, severing myself from my origins and my kind
            <step:σ xmlns:step='data:,wayscript.bit.step'>
